<a href="/questions/844590-what-follows-eventide-did-mr-haruf-bring">What follows Eventide? Did Mr. Haruf bring in some of the key characters; Raymond McPheron, Victoria Roubideaux, Maggie Jones and Tom Guthrie?</a>
