<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/1011913-jo">Jo</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Not really. They&apos;re all mentioned in passing, but the story centers instead around a new cast of characters: Reverend Lyle and his son, John Wesley; &quot;<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Not really. They're all mentioned in passing, but the story centers instead around a new cast of characters: Reverend Lyle and his son, John Wesley; "Dad" Lewis and his wife and daughter; and their neighbor's granddaughter Alice.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
